<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7031786>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Lutosa goeldiana male. A. Habitus in lateral and B. dorsal view. C. Face. D. Terminalia in dorsal view. E. Detail of apex of subgenital plate. F. Subgenital plate. (Photos: J. Hollier)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7031786/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7031770>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Lutosa quaresmai n. sp. male. A. Habitus in lateral and B. dorsal view. C. Face. D–G. Terminalia in dorsal, axial, ventral and lateral views respectively. H. Cerci and lateral plate of last tergite in lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7031770/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7031782>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Lutosa cubaensis male. A. Face and legs in frontal view. B–E. Terminalia in dorsal, lateral, axian and ventral view. (Photos: L. Willemse)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7031782/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7031792>
    dc:description "FIGURE 10. Lutosa paranaensis female. A. Habitus in lateral view. B. Face. C. Head and thorax in lateral view (see the absence of tympana). D. Terminalia in dorsal view. E. Subgenital plate. F. Ovipositor in lateral view. (Photos B. Garcete)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7031792/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7031780>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Lutosa cubaensis male. A. Habitus in lateral and B. dorsal view. (Photos: Luc Willemse)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7031780/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

